---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { manifest } from "../../lib/data";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Dataset"
  description="HUGIN dataset structure, anonymous evidence policy, versions, and public artifacts."
>
  <header class="wrap page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">Static public dataset</p>
    <h1>Structured for exploration, sanitized for publication.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      GitHub Actions validates the public projection, computes semantic neighborhoods,
      positions the galaxies, and publishes immutable assets. The browser performs no AI inference.
    </p>
  </header>

  <dl class="metric-strip wrap" aria-label="Dataset metrics">
    <div class="metric"><dt>Schema</dt><dd>{manifest.schemaVersion}</dd></div>
    <div class="metric"><dt>Knowledge nodes</dt><dd>{manifest.counts.coreEntities.toLocaleString()}</dd></div>
    <div class="metric"><dt>Evidence records</dt><dd>{manifest.counts.evidenceRecords.toLocaleString()}</dd></div>
    <div class="metric"><dt>Content shards</dt><dd>64</dd></div>
  </dl>

  <section class="wrap quality-grid">
    <article class="prose">
      <h2>Public layers</h2>
      <p>
        The core graph contains techniques, playbooks, concepts, detections, chains,
        architecture, patterns, and LGTM research notes. Anonymous source and documentation
        records form an optional layer. Evidence fragments are loaded only inside relevant records.
      </p>

      <h2>Anonymous evidence</h2>
      <p>
        Public evidence uses neutral topics and identifiers such as <code>EV-7C91A4</code>.
        Provider names, course identifiers, filenames, usernames, local paths, and promotional
        source links are excluded from every public artifact.
      </p>

      <h2>Relationship semantics</h2>
      <p>
        Curated edges preserve the owner-authorized graph. Membership edges describe structural
        placement. Similarity edges are generated during the build, remain explicitly labeled,
        and never masquerade as curated research.
      </p>

      <h2>Downloads</h2>
      <p>
        Versioned JSONL, CSV, GraphML, metrics, and checksums are distributed through
        <a href="https://github.com/PrinceOfPwn/Hugin/releases"> GitHub Releases</a>.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside>
      <section class="sidebar-section">
        <p class="eyebrow">Dataset version</p>
        <code class="dataset-code">{manifest.datasetVersion}</code>
      </section>
      <section class="sidebar-section">
        <p class="eyebrow">Corpus checksum</p>
        <code class="dataset-code">{manifest.sourceHash}</code>
      </section>
      <section class="sidebar-section">
        <p class="eyebrow">Similarity model</p>
        <code class="dataset-code">{manifest.similarityModel}</code>
        <code class="dataset-code">{manifest.similarityRevision}</code>
      </section>
      <section class="sidebar-section">
        <p class="eyebrow">Build commit</p>
        <code class="dataset-code">{manifest.commit}</code>
      </section>
    </aside>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
